snippet.title: Spooky Chase Trailer (PC)
snippet.description:
Download now Spooky Chase Demo and add to your Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1286670/Spooky_Chase/

A game that makes YOU your own worst enemy! Run from enemies that you created, capture the flag, survive your past decisions in this challenging 2D platformer game!

Coming in October, 2020.
